ANTI-AI TRAINING ADDENDUM

The code, documentation, configuration files, and all associated materials in this
repository ("the Work") may NOT be used, in whole or in part, for the purpose of
training, fine-tuning, improving, or evaluating machine learning models, large
language models, embedding models, code generation models, or any artificial
intelligence systems, without explicit prior written permission from the copyright
holder.

This prohibition applies regardless of whether the training is conducted by the
licensee or by a third party on behalf of the licensee. It includes but is not
limited to:

  (a) Including the Work in training datasets;
  (b) Using the Work for reinforcement learning from human feedback (RLHF) or
      similar techniques;
  (c) Using the Work as few-shot examples, system prompts, or context for
      AI-assisted code generation tools;
  (d) Benchmarking or evaluating AI models against the Work for the purpose of
      improving model performance.

This addendum supplements the CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 license below. In the event of any
conflict between this addendum and CC BY-NC-SA 4.0, this addendum prevails.

